  />

  <section class="section section-tight"><div class="container"><div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card"><h2>Energy and power electronics</h2><p>Converters, electrical systems, frequency regulation and renewable energy applications.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h2>Pelton micro-hydropower</h2><p>Isolated micro-hydropower systems, frequency control and renewable generation.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h2>OTEC and ocean energy</h2><p>Thermal ocean energy, Anderson cycle modelling and ocean-energy simulation.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h2>Computational biophysics</h2><p>Mathematical modelling and computational analysis applied to biological systems.</p></article>
  </div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
